section.def:
Chapter IV (《第IV章》)
            means Chapter IV of the Annex to the SOLAS Convention, as from time to time revised or
            amended by any revision or amendment that applies to Hong Kong;

sea area A1 (A1海區)
            means a sea area within the radiotelephone coverage of at least one Very High Frequency
            coast station in which continuous digital selective calling alerting is available;

STCW Convention (《培訓公約》) means the International Convention on Standards of Training,
            Certification and Watchkeeping for Seafarers, 1978, as amended from time to time and as
            applicable to Hong Kong;

paragraph.content:
a summary of all the radiocommunications relating to any distress, urgency
                    and safety traffic of the ship together with the time of the
                    communications;
